**José Manuel Barroso**

For the Portuguese footballer, see [José Barroso (footballer)](/Jos%C3%A9_Barroso_(footballer)). For other people, see [Manuel Barroso (disambguation)](/Manuel_Barroso_(disambguation)).

In this [Portuguese name](/Portuguese_name), the first or maternal [family name](/Surname) is [Durão](/Dur%C3%A3o_(surname)) and the second or paternal family name is [Barroso](/Barroso_(surname)).

